description: Kana is another one of the girls who lives in the same dormitory building as Mizuho, who becomes her Oneesama. Kana is more than happy to serve Mizuho any way she can, since she admires him immensely. Kana, who like Yukari is a first-year student, has been waiting for the chance to have an Oneesama as she has always been envious of Yukari having Mariya to fill that role.
name: Suouin Kana
